00:10:08.100 --> 00:10:11.880
lets you know when you're on
track and when you're off.

00:10:11.880 --> 00:10:12.750
It's a compass.

00:10:12.750 --> 00:10:13.380
That's it.

00:10:13.380 --> 00:10:16.030
