or maintain a healthy weight,

00:10:16.030 --> 00:10:17.220
the scale will tell
you, hey, you've

00:10:17.220 --> 00:10:19.386
got to make some changes,
or you're doing just fine.

00:10:19.386 --> 00:10:20.010
That's it.

00:10:20.010 --> 00:10:20.880
It's a barometer.

00:10:20.880 --> 00:10:22.290
That's all that it is.

00:10:22.290 --> 00:10:25.000
And calories are
units of energy.

00:10:25.000 --> 00:10:27.079
So if you consume
more units of energy

00:10:27.079 --> 00:10:29.370
than you're burning in a day,
you will store it as fat.

00:10:29.370 --> 00:10:31.530
