we talked about
where you've been

00:18:59.390 --> 00:19:01.880
and what you've been
doing most recently.

00:19:01.880 --> 00:19:03.560
Can you share-- or
make a prediction

00:19:03.560 --> 00:19:06.470
on where this whole
fitness industry is headed?

00:19:06.470 --> 00:19:10.250
JILLIAN MICHAELS:
[EXHALES] God, there's

00:19:10.250 --> 00:19:15.454
some things I see that
really distress me.

00:19:15.454 --> 00:19:16.870
And then there's
some things I see

00:19:16.870 --> 00:19:18.550
that I'm really hopeful about.

00:19:18.550 --> 00:19:21.640
You know, I love the
integration of technology,

00:19:21.640 --> 00:19:23.800
because information
is power, right?

00:19:23.800 --> 00:19:27.770
And I always tell people, if
you have the right information,

00:19:27.770 --> 00:19:29.260
you can make choices
that are going

00:19:29.260 --> 00:19:31.240
to yield powerful results.

00:19:31.240 --> 00:19:34.632
We get so confused thinking
that action and intention are

00:19:34.632 --> 00:19:35.590
going to bring results.

00:19:35.590 --> 00:19:37.640
But, in truth, if you
take misinformed action,

00:19:37.640 --> 00:19:39.020
you'll have disaster.

00:19:39.020 --> 00:19:42.540
But if you take informed, very
deliberate, specific actions,

00:19:42.540 --> 00:19:45.006
and you make informed
choices, you're

00:19:45.006 --> 00:19:48.220
going to get, most of the time,
really positive and powerful

00:19:48.220 --> 00:19:49.100
outcomes.

00:19:49.100 --> 00:19:50.980
So I love that
technology is giving us

00:19:50.980 --> 00:19:54.635
this kind of information
now, so we can see, like, OK,

00:19:54.635 --> 00:19:56.510
you know, you're not
working out hard enough.

00:19:56.510 --> 00:19:57.550
Your heart rate's here.

