You can tell when people
have more, oh, I'm dying.

00:20:03.190 --> 00:20:05.280
Yeah, your heart rate's
at 75; you're not dying.

00:20:05.280 --> 00:20:06.280
You know, just various--

00:20:06.280 --> 00:20:08.750
how far they walked, how
much they've done, like,

00:20:08.750 --> 00:20:09.930
that stuff's exciting.

00:20:09.930 --> 00:20:11.200
You know, how much they slept.

00:20:11.200 --> 00:20:12.530
How much they had deep sleep.

00:20:12.530 --> 00:20:15.370
How much hydration
they have, and so on.

00:20:15.370 --> 00:20:18.660
The part that is distressing
for me-- and I, honest to God,

00:20:18.660 --> 00:20:23.890
cannot tell if I'm
